001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import java.time.Instant;
004import java.util.List;
005import java.util.Optional;
006
007import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
008import org.bitcoinj.base.Address;
009
010public class AddressInfo {
011    private final Address address;
012    private final String scriptPubKey;
013    private final boolean ismine;
014    private final boolean solvable;
015    private final String desc;
016    private final boolean iswatchonly;
017    private final boolean isscript;
018    private final boolean iswitness;
019    private final String pubkey;
020    private final boolean iscompressed;
021    private final String label;
022    private final boolean ischange;
023    private final Instant timestamp;
024    private final List<Object> labels;
025
026    /**
027     *
028     * @param address
029     * @param ischange
030     * @param ismine
031     * @param label
032     * @param iswatchonly
033     * @param iswitness
034     * @param labels
035     * @param scriptPubKey
036     * @param solvable
037     * @param isscript
038     * @param iscompressed
039     * @param desc
040     * @param pubkey
041     * @param timestamp
042     */
043    public AddressInfo(@JsonProperty("address") Address address,
044                       @JsonProperty("scriptPubKey") String scriptPubKey,
045                       @JsonProperty("ismine") boolean ismine,
046                       @JsonProperty("solvable") boolean solvable,
047                       @JsonProperty("desc") String desc,
048                       @JsonProperty("iswatchonly") boolean iswatchonly,
049                       @JsonProperty("isscript") boolean isscript,
050                       @JsonProperty("iswitness") boolean iswitness,
051                       @JsonProperty("pubkey") String pubkey,
052                       @JsonProperty("iscompressed") boolean iscompressed,
053                       @JsonProperty("label") String label,
054                       @JsonProperty("ischange") boolean ischange,
055                       @JsonProperty("timestamp") Long timestamp,
056                       @JsonProperty("labels") List<Object> labels) {
057        super();
058        this.address = address;
059        this.scriptPubKey = scriptPubKey;
060        this.ismine = ismine;
061        this.solvable = solvable;
062        this.desc = desc;
063        this.iswatchonly = iswatchonly;
064        this.isscript = isscript;
065        this.iswitness = iswitness;
066        this.pubkey = pubkey;
067        this.iscompressed = iscompressed;
068        this.label = label;
069        this.ischange = ischange;
070        this.timestamp = timestamp != null ? Instant.ofEpochSecond(timestamp) : null;
071        this.labels = labels;
072    }
073
074    public Address getAddress() {
075        return address;
076    }
077
078    public String getScriptPubKey() {
079        return scriptPubKey;
080    }
081
082    public boolean getIsmine() {
083        return ismine;
084    }
085
086    public boolean getSolvable() {
087        return solvable;
088    }
089
090    public String getDesc() {
091        return desc;
092    }
093
094    public boolean getIswatchonly() {
095        return iswatchonly;
096    }
097
098    public boolean getIsscript() {
099        return isscript;
100    }
101
102    public boolean getIswitness() {
103        return iswitness;
104    }
105
106    public String getPubkey() {
107        return pubkey;
108    }
109
110    public boolean getIscompressed() {
111        return iscompressed;
112    }
113
114    public String getLabel() {
115        return label;
116    }
117
118    public boolean getIschange() {
119        return ischange;
120    }
121
122    /**
123     * @return The creation time of the key, if available
124     */
125    public Optional<Instant> getTimestamp() {
126        return Optional.ofNullable(timestamp);
127    }
128
129    public List<Object> getLabels() {
130        return labels;
131    }
132}
